title: Sticky Lemongrass Ginger Beef & Pork Meatballs with Cucumber Slaw & Ponzu Mayo Dressing
description: Revisit this classic, but add a signature HelloFresh twist! We’ve created tender honey-soy and ginger lemongrass
glazed beef & pork meatballs, which we add to a vibrant and creamy slaw with an extra burst of flavour from ponzu sauce - a
Japanese pantry staple with a kick of citrus. Sprinkle over some spring onion and go for your life.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
